quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Diggah Yalli Qhiyaamah ayról xiibite
  75,2,Kaadu diggah moominti nafsiy isi yassacakkel xiibite
  75,3,Seehadayti (korosta kinnuk) kay lafoofi gaaboyse weennom yakka lee
  75,4,"Yeey, nanu tet gaaboysenno, kay feeraarih exaaxi massosnam duudak"
  75,5,"Tonna hinnay, seehadayti isi foocal tanim dirabboysam faxa"
  75,6,Qhiyaamah ayró maa waqdii iyyeh esseraamal? (kah esseram anqasa)
  75,7,Tokkel Mablá baditta waqdi
  75,8,Kaadu alsá diifi duugumta waqdi
  75,9,Kaadu ayroó kee alsá gaaboysimtaah inki arac yawqen waqdi
  75,10,"Seehadayti: woo ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) anke kudnaa anke eleelitnaa iyya"
  75,11,Tonna hinnay eleelitan rike matan
  75,12,Woo ayró idyaa kee madab ku Rabbih xaqu cagalah
  75,13,Seehadaytuh woo ayró taamak yuysukumem kee wadirroysem warsintah
  75,14,"Tonna hinnay, seehadayti isi nafsil isih sumaaqita"
  75,15,Kaadu Abeh yan uma taamak faxem malkitaamah woo malkit kaah xiqam mali
  75,16,"Nabiyow wacyi kol ooba waqdi qhuraanat isi arraba masgayyin, raqsat kaak tasissikeemih fayxih"
  75,17,"Diggah nel tan kaa liilil kaa gaabosnam, kee kay kiraati"
  75,18,"Kaadu Nabiyow ni farmoyti jibriil gitak qhuraan kol nakriye waqdi, kaa ankacisaay tibbi ixxic, tohuk lakal usuk koo elle barse innal ikriy"
  75,19,Tohuk lakal diggah kay baxxaqisiyyi nel yan
  75,20,"Korosey caagid Isin elle takkalen inna hinna, ugut kee galtok tu matana ittaanamal, nummah isin addunyaa kee tet bilhada kicinton"
  75,21,"Kaadu isin akeera cabtaanaah, teetih mataamittan"
  75,22,Woo ayró meqe marih Foocitte (qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) iftah
  75,23,Isi Rabbî fanah wagitta.(woh meqe mara kinnuk)
  75,24,Kaadu woo ayró uma marih foocitte ribbimtah
  75,25,Kaxxa umaanéy xiiron lafoofi teetik edde taddigillee teetit akke lem tasmiteh
  75,26,Nummah rooci (coxxo) kaxkaxxo gufa waqdi
  75,27,Iyyi kaa daylisaa iyyan
  75,28,Kaadu diggah usuk (raba num) addunyak baxsimam yasmiteh. (raba kinnuk)
  75,29,Kaadu sarba sarbat makitta
  75,30,Woo ayro (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) seehadak beyto ku Rabbî fanah takke